data.description:
Airy, unbroken spaces characterize this inspired ranch home in Eagle Crest Ranch. The formal dining room opens onto a well-appointed kitchen, which is separated from the breakfast nook only by an expansive central island. The nook then flows uninterrupted into the living room, completing this comfortable, functional area.

Brokered And Advertised By: Richmond American Homes
Listing Agent: Daniel V Tartabini
